SUMMARY:Tai Chi: Moving Meditation
DTSTAMP:20260325T091631Z
DTSTART:20260326T090000Z
DESCRIPTION:Come have fun! Build strength\\\, balance\\\, and agility with 
	the centuries-old practices of Tai Chi and Qigong. Experience deep breathi
	ng\\\, slow flowing movement\\\, and meditation to maximize longevity and 
	improve quality of life. Suitable for all ability levels. Taught by Larry 
	Spangler. Register: 206.297.0875.\n\nhttps://www.phinneycenter.org/event/t
